{"id":614440,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/07/【网络民议】只有点赞，没有悲伤/","date":"2019-07-24T17:58:02Z","modified":"2019-07-24T17:58:02Z","title":"【网络民议】只有点赞，没有悲伤","content":"<p>CDT编者按：中国前国务院总理李鹏于北京时间2019年7月22日23时11分在北京去世，终年91岁。因六四镇压，三峡大坝和家族成员被指以权谋私等事件，李鹏的去世在大陆网络上引起一片点赞，新华社在新浪微博发布的讣告不得不关闭点赞功能。网友评论：只有点赞，没有悲伤。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-614441\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/1-33.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/1-33.jpg 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/1-33-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-614442\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/2-21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/2-21.jpg 602w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/2-21-300x230.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-614443\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/3-17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/3-17.jpg 488w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/3-17-183x300.jpg 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-614444\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/image_from_ios-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/image_from_ios-3.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/image_from_ios-3-300x179.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/image_from_ios-3-768x457.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/image_from_ios-3-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-61444